  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the feasibility of aspiration samples for mutational
      analysis in patients with a non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will compare results of mutational analysis from a core needle biopsy and
      fine needle aspiration.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
